<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 15:11:18 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Polestar 融资近 10 亿美元，预计 2024 年利润率将有所改善</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/polestar-raises-almost-1-bln-sees-margins-improving-2024-2024-02-28/</link><description>Polestar周三表示，已从一家银行财团筹集了9.5亿美元贷款，有助于填补沃尔沃汽车表示将停止向这家电动汽车制造商提供资金后留下的资金缺口。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 14:22:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/polestar-raises-almost-1-bln-sees-margins-improving-2024-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>印度和南非在世贸组织谈判中阻止投资协议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india-south-africa-block-investment-deal-wto-talks-2024-02-28/</link><description>一份文件显示，代表们周三确认，印度和南非已在阿布扎比举行的世界贸易组织会议上对一项投资协议提出正式反对意见，阻止该协议的通过。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 14:21:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india-south-africa-block-investment-deal-wto-talks-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>印度在世贸组织会议上寻求农业和争端制度改革</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-seeks-reforms-agriculture-disputes-system-wto-meeting-2024-02-28/</link><description>印度贸易部长周三表示，印度希望本周在阿布扎比举行的高级别会议上就农业改革的关键内容以及恢复世界贸易组织的仲裁权达成协议。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 14:01:21 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/india-seeks-reforms-agriculture-disputes-system-wto-meeting-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>意大利与特斯拉等公司洽谈寻找第二家汽车制造商</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-talks-tesla-others-search-second-carmaker-2024-02-28/</link><description>意大利工业部长周三表示，意大利一直在与特斯拉和其他汽车制造商（包括亚洲国家的汽车制造商）进行谈判，试图吸引另一家制造商并实现 130 万辆汽车的年产量目标。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 13:53:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-talks-tesla-others-search-second-carmaker-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>共和党参议员希望提高对中国汽车的关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/republican-senator-wants-hike-tariffs-chinese-vehicles-2024-02-28/</link><description>由于人们越来越担心这些汽车对美国汽车公司的影响，共和党参议员乔什·霍利周三提出立法，提高对中国汽车的进口关税。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 12:06:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/republican-senator-wants-hike-tariffs-chinese-vehicles-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>中国总理李克强敦促加强与美国的经贸关系</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-premier-li-urges-stronger-economic-trade-ties-with-us-2024-02-28/</link><description>据中国国家广播电台报道，中国国务院总理李强周三在会见来访的美国代表团时表示，中美应加强经贸关系，华盛顿应避免与中国脱钩。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:36:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/chinas-premier-li-urges-stronger-economic-trade-ties-with-us-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：美国增长 3% 以上；苹果降档，新西兰惊喜</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-28/</link><description>迈克·多兰 (Mike Dolan) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:02:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>大众汽车称长安汽车前首席软件架构师将出任Cariad中国新任首席执行官</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-says-changan-auto-former-chief-software-architect-be-new-cariad-china-2024-02-28/</link><description>大众汽车周三表示，长安汽车前首席软件架构师韩弗兰克将于 3 月 1 日接任 Cariad 中国首席执行官。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 11:01:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/volkswagen-says-changan-auto-former-chief-software-architect-be-new-cariad-china-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>拜登将打击美国数据流向中国和俄罗斯</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/biden-crack-down-us-data-flows-china-russia-2024-02-28/</link><description>美国高级官员表示，出于国家安全考虑，总统拜登政府周三公布了一项行政命令，旨在通过限制向中国、俄罗斯和其他国家传输美国个人数据来保护美国个人数据。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 10:02:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/biden-crack-down-us-data-flows-china-russia-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>情报局长表示，澳大利亚政客向外国间谍团伙“出卖”了国家</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-intelligence-chief-reveals-details-foreign-spy-operation-2024-02-28/</link><description>该国间谍负责人周三表示，一名前政客将澳大利亚“出卖”给了外国情报机构，并补充说，他的机构已与间谍团伙对峙，让他们知道他们的身份已被揭穿。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 09:13:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-intelligence-chief-reveals-details-foreign-spy-operation-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>人工智能和广告推动业务增长，百度第四季度收入增长 6%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-baidu-quarterly-revenue-misses-estimates-2024-02-28/</link><description>中国百度表示，得益于人工智能应用和不断增长的广告业务的增长，第四季度收入增长了 6%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 09:05:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/chinas-baidu-quarterly-revenue-misses-estimates-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>欧洲国家考虑在大流行关闭后重新开放驻朝鲜大使馆</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/european-countries-eye-reopening-embassies-north-korea-after-pandemic-closures-2024-02-28/</link><description>德国代表团自朝鲜大使馆在疫情期间关闭以来首次访问朝鲜首都平壤，而其他欧洲国家则在为预期的回归做准备。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 08:38:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/european-countries-eye-reopening-embassies-north-korea-after-pandemic-closures-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>消息人士称，Kedaara 即将为印度最大的私募基金筹集 17 亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/india/kedaara-close-raising-17-bln-indias-biggest-pe-fund-sources-say-2024-02-28/</link><description>两位直接了解情况的人士表示，Kedaara Capital 计划为印度有史以来最大的私募股权基金筹集 17 亿美元，这突显了印度经济从中国转移出去的情况下对该国快速增长的经济的巨大兴趣。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 06:51:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/india/kedaara-close-raising-17-bln-indias-biggest-pe-fund-sources-say-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾特使表示，特朗普担任总统期间印太立场没有变化</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/no-change-indo-pacific-stance-under-trump-presidency-says-philippine-envoy-2024-02-28/</link><description>菲律宾长期驻华盛顿大使周三表示，如果唐纳德·特朗普赢得 11 月份的总统竞选，美国的印太战略不太可能改变。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 06:10:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/no-change-indo-pacific-stance-under-trump-presidency-says-philippine-envoy-2024-02-28/</guid></item><item><title>由于对自由的担忧，香港准备制定更严格的安全法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-moves-towards-enacting-tougher-security-law-amid-concerns-about-2024-02-28/</link><description>香港新国家安全法的公众咨询期于周三结束，人们担心当局希望尽快实施的这项立法将进一步侵蚀这个金融中心的自由。</description><pubDate>Wed, 28 Feb 2024 05:48:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-moves-towards-enacting-tougher-security-law-amid-concerns-about-2024-02-28/</guid></item></channel></rss>